<section class="section service border-top">
	<div class="container">
		<div class="row justify-content-center">
			<div class="col-lg-7 text-center">
				<div class="section-title">
					<span class="h6 color-four">Our Services</span>
					<h2 class="mt-3 content-title ">We provide a wide range of financial services </h2>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="row justify-content-center">
			<div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-sm-6">
				<div class="service-item mb-5">
					<i class="ti-wallet color-four"></i>
					<h4 class="mb-3">Checking accounts</h4>
					<p>We serve up free interest-bearing checking accounts with no strings attached.</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-sm-6">
				<div class="service-item mb-5">
					<i class="ti-time color-four"></i>
					<h4 class="mb-3">Savings accounts.</h4>
					<p>Our savings accounts come with a low interest rate, their safety and reliability make them a great option for parking cash you want available for short-term needs.</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-sm-6">
				<div class="service-item mb-5">
					<i class="ti-credit-card color-four"></i>
					<h4 class="mb-3">Debit & credit cards</h4>
					<p>Globally supported cards, that can be used for both withrawals and deposits.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-sm-6">
				<div class="service-item mb-5 mb-lg-0">
					<i class="ti-vector color-four"></i>
					<h4 class="mb-3">Insurance</h4>
					<p>We offer housing, salary and life insurance.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-sm-6">
				<div class="service-item mb-5 mb-lg-0">
					<i class="ti-crown color-four"></i>
					<h4 class="mb-3">Wealth management</h4>
					<p>Our management is in world class, speak to your local banker to set up an appointment.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			
		</div>
